SwerveSubsystem.driveToPose() returns a Command that must be scheduled. You will have to completely restructure your rightAlign Command. I would recommend creating a m_currentCommand variable which is assigned to the command determined by your heading logic during initialize. rightAlignâ€™s init, execute, isFinished, ect should all call the m_currentCommandâ€™s respective methods.
